            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 hover:bg-[#1e1f23] cursor-pointer">
            <p class="font-semibold text-white">
              Le Rwanda
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
              5 629 publications
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 hover:bg-[#1e1f23] cursor-pointer">
            <p class="font-semibold text-white">
              AS Monaco
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
              3 586 publications
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#16181c] rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold px-4 py-3">
            Vous pourriez aimer
          </h2>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 hover:bg-[#1e1f23] flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-white">
                *Urbano*
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                @Urbano_N
              </p>
            </div>
            <button class="bg-white text-black px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">
              Suivre
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 hover:bg-[#1e1f23] flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-white">
                Bernard BAHATI
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                @Bernard_bahati
              </p>
            </div>
            <button class="bg-white text-black px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">
              Suivre
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 hover:bg-[#1e1f23] flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-white">
                Billy
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                @RebeuDeter
